WEBVTT


01:16:57.529 --> 01:17:01.074 line:85.83%,end
Film every single hostage
including the doctor.

01:17:01.158 --> 01:17:02.743 line:85.83%,end
An hour will be enough, right?

01:17:03.201 --> 01:17:04.995 line:85.83%,end
I'll radio you once I'm done.

01:17:06.580 --> 01:17:07.539 line:85.83%,end
What about the proof?

01:17:12.794 --> 01:17:15.172 line:85.83%,end
I need to see my team leader first.

01:17:15.756 --> 01:17:17.466 line:85.83%,end
Your fiancé is safe, so don't worry.

01:17:18.925 --> 01:17:20.218 line:85.83%,end
It'll only take a minute.

01:17:20.886 --> 01:17:23.555 line:85.83%,end
I risked my life to get this.
You can't even allow me a minute?

01:17:27.309 --> 01:17:30.103 line:85.83%,end
All right, fine. I'll just give it to you.

01:17:41.490 --> 01:17:43.825 line:85.83%,end
In order to obtain this, a person is

01:17:45.535 --> 01:17:47.204 line:85.83%,end
dying in the interrogation room
of the ANSP.

01:17:48.914 --> 01:17:49.998 line:85.83%,end
So listen to it carefully.

01:17:51.083 --> 01:17:52.918 line:85.83%,end
I've brought this to you

01:17:53.919 --> 01:17:55.337 line:85.83%,end
because I think you're different

01:17:55.420 --> 01:17:57.631 line:85.83%,end
from Geum-cheol
who killed himself with cyanide.

01:18:08.350 --> 01:18:09.351 line:85.83%,end
Hey.

01:18:09.893 --> 01:18:14.398 line:85.83%,end
Shouldn't you at least give water
to Yeong-ro and Ms. Pi?

01:18:16.233 --> 01:18:17.818 line:85.83%,end
How long will you keep us tied up?

01:18:26.118 --> 01:18:27.661 line:85.83%,end
Comrade Kang wants to see you.

01:18:28.286 --> 01:18:29.913 line:85.83%,end
Tell her I'll radio the party first.

01:18:33.083 --> 01:18:34.292 line:85.83%,end
Lim Soo-ho.

01:18:34.376 --> 01:18:36.545 line:85.83%,end
We're rats in a trap!

01:18:37.254 --> 01:18:38.630 line:85.83%,end
Rats in a trap.

01:18:55.772 --> 01:18:57.733 line:85.83%,end
<i>Did you forget about the agreement?</i>

01:18:57.899 --> 01:19:02.070 line:85.83%,end
<i>We agreed to killing all the spies</i>

01:19:02.320 --> 01:19:04.865 line:85.83%,end
<i>and saving the hostages. Right?</i>

01:19:08.785 --> 01:19:10.662 line:85.83%,end
<i>Did you forget about the agreement?</i>

01:19:10.954 --> 01:19:15.167 line:85.83%,end
<i>We agreed to killing all the spies.</i>

01:19:21.381 --> 01:19:22.799 line:85.83%,end
<i>Enemies are everywhere.</i>

01:19:23.300 --> 01:19:26.595 line:85.83%,end
Those who have power
all thanks to their family name

01:19:26.678 --> 01:19:28.805 line:85.83%,end
have their guns pointed at me.

01:19:28.889 --> 01:19:33.393 line:85.83%,end
You're my last weapon
that I can kill them with.

01:19:33.477 --> 01:19:34.895 line:85.83%,end
Don't forget that.

01:19:38.565 --> 01:19:40.734 line:85.83%,end
If my father has been suspended…

01:19:42.235 --> 01:19:43.236 line:85.83%,end
<i>Right.</i>

01:19:44.070 --> 01:19:45.405 line:85.83%,end
<i>That must be it.</i>

01:19:45.906 --> 01:19:48.366 line:85.83%,end
<i>It must have been someone else's decision.</i>

01:19:49.826 --> 01:19:51.453 line:85.83%,end
<i>There's no way my father would…</i>

01:20:37.207 --> 01:20:38.750 line:85.83%,end
Ryesong River 1, can you hear me?

01:20:39.876 --> 01:20:42.045 line:85.83%,end
<i>Ryesong River 1, loud and clear.</i>

01:20:44.464 --> 01:20:46.383 line:85.83%,end
Any change in the location
of Mount Myohyang?

01:21:11.283 --> 01:21:12.325 line:85.83%,end
What were you doing?

01:21:14.411 --> 01:21:15.996 line:85.83%,end
I radioed the message about your cover

01:21:16.079 --> 01:21:18.373 line:85.83%,end
being blown and asked what to do about it.

01:21:18.540 --> 01:21:20.750 line:85.83%,end
But there was no reply,
so I was about to do it again.

01:21:24.087 --> 01:21:25.547 line:85.83%,end
It's an important matter,

01:21:25.630 --> 01:21:27.841 line:85.83%,end
so it must be taking them
quite a while to discuss.

01:21:29.217 --> 01:21:30.093 line:85.83%,end
Oh, right.

01:21:32.053 --> 01:21:34.806 line:85.83%,end
Does the party know
the ANSP director's daughter is here?

01:21:36.975 --> 01:21:38.143 line:85.83%,end
They do.

